*
     * Adds text column to table
     *
     * @param {string} attr - attribute name
     * @param {string} name - column name
     * @returns {TextCellConfigurator}

     * @memberOf TableBuilder

     *
     * @param {string} attr - attribute name
     * @param {string} name - column name

     *
     * @memberOf TableBuilder
     * @example
     * tableBuilder.addAction('id', t('Remove'))
